export const commandRunner=command=>{switch(command.type){case'navigate':window.open(command.url,'_blank');break;case'copy':navigator.clipboard.writeText(command.textToCopy).then(()=>alert('Copied to clipboard')).catch(err=>console.error('Failed to copy text: ',err));break;default:console.error('Unknown command type');}};
